# ─── RugTown environment variables ──────────────────────────────────────────
# Copy this file to .env.local (which is gitignored) and fill in real values.
# Never commit .env.local or any file containing real keys.

# ─── Supabase ────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Get these from: Supabase dashboard → your project → Settings → API
#
# VITE_SUPABASE_URL      — the project's REST/Realtime endpoint
# VITE_SUPABASE_ANON_KEY — the public anon key (safe to expose in the browser;
#                          Postgres Row-Level Security policies enforce access control)
#
# Without these two variables RugTown runs in guest-only mode:
# all gameplay works, but progress is not saved between sessions.
#
# ⚠  Do NOT paste the service_role key here — it must never reach client code.

VITE_SUPABASE_URL=https://your-project-id.supabase.co
VITE_SUPABASE_ANON_KEY=your-anon-public-key-here
